OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772798583
OL,3,CMan, 87, waited two days for air
OL,4,Cambulance after heart attack
OL,6,FA man who had to wait two days to be
OL,7,Ftransferred to Guernsey's Princess
OL,8,FElizabeth Hospital after having a
OL,9,Fheart attack in Alderney says the
OL,10,Fdelay could have killed him.
OL,12,FMartin Smith, 87, suffered an angina
OL,13,Fattack on Sunday (1 March) and would
OL,14,Fnormally have been taken by a medevac
OL,15,Fplane operated by the airline Aurigny.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772798583
OL,3,CMan, 87, waited two days for air
OL,4,Cambulance after heart attack
OL,6,FHowever, the new Twin Otter aircraft,
OL,7,Fwhich have replaced the Dorniers,
OL,8,Fcurrently cannot handle these transfer
OL,9,Fflights and the backup Skybus Islander
OL,10,Fwas stranded at Land's End in the UK
OL,11,Fdue to bad weather.
OL,13,FThe Flying Christine III marine
OL,14,Fambulance, which is used for medical
OL,15,Fevacuations by sea, is also out of
OL,16,Faction for engineering work.
OL,18,FMartin was eventually transferred to
OL,19,FGuernsey by charter boat on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772798583
OL,3,CMan, 87, waited two days for air
OL,4,Cambulance after heart attack
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Channel about the
OL,7,Fordeal, Martin said: "If my heart
OL,8,Fattack had been as serious as it
OL,9,Fcould've been, I'd have been dead.
OL,11,F"It scared me to death, I'm telling
OL,12,Fyou. And now, just that these people
OL,13,Fwho make silly decisions, who don't
OL,14,Funderstand what life is about."
OL,16,FMartin's niece, Alex Flewitt, added
OL,17,Fthat the family were speaking out for
OL,18,Fthe benefit of others who may be
OL,19,Fimpacted.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772798583
OL,3,CMan, 87, waited two days for air
OL,4,Cambulance after heart attack
OL,6,FShe explained: "We know how difficult
OL,7,Fit is living on such a small island,
OL,8,Fand we know we rely on things like the
OL,9,Fmedevacs to get us to the hospitals
OL,10,Fand the medical professionals - we
OL,11,Fjust don't want to see this happen to
OL,12,Fanybody else.
OL,14,F"We're very concerned that in the
OL,15,Ffuture, should there be a major
OL,16,Fincident, should there be a road
OL,17,Ftraffic collision, it's an amount of
OL,18,Ftime. If someone has a stroke or a
OL,19,Fheart attack, you have to act fast and
OL,20,Fon this occasion, speed was certainly
OL,21,Fnot of the essence."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772798583
OL,3,CMan, 87, waited two days for air
OL,4,Cambulance after heart attack
OL,6,FAurigny recently promised that one of
OL,7,Fits Twin Otter aircraft, which
OL,8,Foperates the airline's lifeline
OL,9,Fservices between Guernsey and
OL,10,FAlderney, would be equipped to run
OL,11,Fmedical evacuations.
OL,13,FIn a statement, the company said the
OL,14,Fplane had not yet been fitted with
OL,15,Fstretcher lifts to transfer patients
OL,16,Fsafely when Martin had the heart
OL,17,Fattack.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772798583
OL,3,CMan, 87, waited two days for air
OL,4,Cambulance after heart attack
OL,6,FPhilip Smallwood, Chief Operations
OL,7,FOfficer for Aurigny, added: "In the
OL,8,Fpast week, Alderney, Guernsey and
OL,9,FSouthampton have each received the
OL,10,Fnecessary stretcher lifts required to
OL,11,Ffacilitate the safe transfer of
OL,12,Fpatients onto the Twin Otter aircraft.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772798583
OL,3,CMan, 87, waited two days for air
OL,4,Cambulance after heart attack
OL,6,F"Earlier this week in Guernsey (3
OL,7,FMarch), alongside Guernsey Ambulance
OL,8,Fand Fire Services, we conducted a
OL,9,Ftrial on the use of the lifts, which
OL,10,Fwas successful. This has been repeated
OL,11,Fin Alderney with the Public Health
OL,12,FServices, together with Alderney's
OL,13,FAmbulance and Fire Services, today (5
OL,14,FMarch).
OL,16,F"Twin Otter medevac services are now
OL,17,Ffully operational, and once again,
OL,18,Fwe're proud to serve our islands with
OL,19,Fany emergency medical needs.
OL,26,@nD@`pmoD@FpnuD@dpmvD@Fpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772798583
OL,3,CMan, 87, waited two days for air
OL,4,Cambulance after heart attack
OL,6,F"The Islander aircraft remains
OL,7,Favailable to be used when required in
OL,8,Fthe event of technical issues with the
OL,9,FTwin Otter."
OL,11,FHowever, Iain MacFarlane, Chairman of
OL,12,Fthe States of Alderney's General
OL,13,FServices Committee, has questioned the
OL,14,Fdelay.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772798583
OL,3,CMan, 87, waited two days for air
OL,4,Cambulance after heart attack
OL,6,FHe explained: "You would have expected
OL,7,Fthat for such a big company, and for
OL,8,Fsuch an important part of that
OL,9,Fcompany, that these issues would have
OL,10,Freally been ironed out before the
OL,11,Foperation of the new aircraft, but
OL,12,Fagain, this isn't to criticise the
OL,13,Fcrews, the pilots of the medical staff
OL,14,For any handling agents or anything.
OL,16,F"They work extremely hard and they
OL,17,Foften do go above and beyond to help
OL,18,Fpassengers."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
